    "(6) Implementation DetailsFor the BERT encoder in DE3TC, we adopt bert-base-uncased in huggingface, 2 which has 768 hidden embedding dimensions and 12 attention layers, and each layer has 12 heads.",
    "We set the hyperparameter K to 2, which means the similar type selector selects the top 2 similar event type descriptions.",
    "The learning rate is 4e-05, the batch size is 8.",
    "We train our models with Adam optimizer [33] and 10% warming-up steps.",
    "Our experiments run on one NVIDIA Geforce RTX 3090."
  ],
